        <item>
            <title>【教学】学生简单重用测验卷+工作纸助温习，一键除答案 + 自由选择题目重印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pastpaper-redo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:00:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[docu scan]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[scanner]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手写]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[扫瞄]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[文件处理]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[消除笔迹]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277763</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">每逢踏入 12 月，不少中、小学生又是时候准备上学期的考试。除了温习教科书之外，不少家长都会购买补充练习来给子女操练，不过因为不同学校教学的内容、深浅度均有所不同，很多时都会出现太深或者太浅，甚至未教未学的情况。最理想的做法当然就是重温小朋友学校做过的工作纸、测验卷或者 Past paper 了。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/afee4d39061f40aaa8d4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">不过，大部份旧功课、测试早已填满答案、甚至已经由老师以红笔批改，不少家长会选择用手、白纸遮掩答案或以对话方式去考验同学的对课本内容的熟悉度，不够方便而且效果亦欠佳。其实大家可以借助现今科技，透过手机 / 平板去把工作纸、测试卷的手写笔迹还原空白，方便同学可以好好温习!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/14b5d5d8abb6443788ab.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c6f0700f8b0a48a78619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">坊间其实有不少扫瞄 app 可以经由手机拍下相片变成 pdf 或其他格式的文件储存，不论是 google play 或是 app store 都可以找到林林总总的选择，而小记亲身试过比较方便，容易操作，而且可以免费使用，可能就是以下介绍的这款「CS 全能扫瞄王」了。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs-694x334.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs-694x334.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cs.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/7f9e56d8bd6344fb8a2a.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><h3><b>超快 3 步操作! </b></h3><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.要消除练习上面的笔迹非常简单，首先在平板/ 手机上打开 CS 全能扫描王，然后在上方的功能列按一下「试卷去手写」（红圈）进入拍摄页面，或者大家亦可以直接由相簿中汇入之前已经拍摄好的试卷或工作纸，程式可以支援多页扫瞄，只需连续拍摄整份试卷便可。另外，大家亦可以</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">按下右下角拍摄键直接拍摄文件，以进行其他更多的编辑功能。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/5ab7bfade93448979aca-1.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fda95f2d9e8b438b8adc.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/73c6592024e9496c959f.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.拍摄前，用家可以选择是否开启闪光灯、解像度等等。没有特别要求的话其实可以让系统自动处理，效果也不会有太大分别。完成拍摄文件后，大家可以看到右下角的相片预览。如果拍摄了超过一张相片则可以见到以橙色数字显示的数目。按一下预览图片，系统便会马上显示已经把手写写迹去除的页面了！</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/65cc4f045fd54b5f9fc0.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.最后，把处理好的文件保存至相片或文件格式，便可以直接利用 Apple Pencil / Stylus 在平板画面做练习，又或是配合打印机 app 直接列印出来给小朋友复习了!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/ec62fdea597b427b8a59.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277800" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/c7950977759e4dc5b3d2.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><h3>进阶改错功能</h3><p>为了照顾不同玩家，例如只想让小朋友重做答错的问题，大家则可以在拍摄文件相片后，按一下下图的（错题组卷），系统会自动把相片中每一条题目和答案栏分开，玩家可以手动把每条想打印出来问题和答案手动选择（按下 + 号）。在下一步选择题目的间距和排列方法便可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d43513bebdb8415eac90.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/f7d2c6a42f3148dbb390.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e64f527f58624fa99f31.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4-327x580.jpg" alt="" width="327" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4-327x580.jpg 327w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/824c89801fbb450cb7a4.jpg 507w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 327px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5-270x580.jpg" alt="" width="270" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5-270x580.jpg 270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/d901394ccbcb452e96c5.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 270px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">用过这个试卷去手写功能后大家就会发现，扫瞄的功课越多手写部份，能够省下的时间和满足感亦更大!</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">值得留意，因为扫瞄后的文件只能以黑白文件显示，如果工作纸练习中有相片或者绘图，往往会比较模糊，甚么系统会误认是笔迹而被清除。试过一些涉及图片的题目即使扫瞄后也不能再做，但是总括来说练习没有并没有大影响。虽然这款「CS 全能扫瞄王」可能需要大家观看广告但是却可以不断的免费使用，相信一定能够帮助各位家长和小朋友考试前温习争取好成绩!</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1277797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/4bf24b22ba2c44b9b4d4-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/pastpaper-redo/fun-tech/">【教学】学生简单重用测验卷+工作纸助温习，一键除答案 + 自由选择题目重印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
